PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the PIAPOT BAND surrenders, for a term conditional on band concil resolution, approximately 8,924 hectares of land within Piapot Indian Reserve No. 75 and Piapot Cree First Nation Indian Reserve Nos. 75"E", 75"F", 75"G", 75"H", 75"I", 75"J" and 75"K" in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of exploration and/or exploitation of oil and/or gas purposes.
